    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Computational Thinking \r\n## (Part 1)\r\n\r\nUse this chatbot to help you with **decomposition** or breaking down your event planning into smaller tasks.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n- Tell the chatbot what event you're planning.\r\n- Ask it to help you brainstorm or clarify what tasks are needed, see examples below.\r\n\r\n**Example Prompts:**\r\n- **Brainstorm:** I'm planning a **school spirit week**. Help me come up with tasks I need to complete.\r\n-  **Clarify:** I know that I will need to **sell tickets for prom**. Help me clarify how to accomplish this task, by giving me 3 subtasks with a one-sentence explanation for each.\r\n\r\n**Tips**:\r\n- To get more ideas, simply ask the chatbot to **\"Come up with 3 more ideas\"**\r\n- If the chatbot's response is too wordy, ask it to **\"Only give a one sentence explanation\"**",
